snippet.title: Nestables - Farming & Building Editor Early Preview
snippet.description:
This video is an early preview of the work that has been completed so far on the farming system and building editor which will be included in the beta of Nestables. Clearly, this is very early footage so not everything is perfect yet! The crop growing times are also for demonstration only.

You can learn more

Song Credit:
Nora En Pure - Trailblazer
